  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures.<br>Assuming a departure/destination fuel price ratio of 0.92, the commander decides to optimize fuel tankering by using the following data:</p><p>Cruise flight level: FL 350\u00a0<br>Air distance to be covered: 1830 NM\u00a0<br>Planned take-off mass: 190 000 kg (with a minimum prescribed fuel quantity of 30 000 kg that includes a trip fuel of 22 000 kg)\u00a0<br>Maximum landing mass: 180 000 kg\u00a0<br>Maximum take-off mass: 205 000 kg\u00a0<br>Maximum tank capacity: 40 000 kg</p><p>The additional fuel quantity will be\u2026</p>",
